{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"baf1e1b922","title":"关于改变一九五一年部队教育时间比例的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e54ee25c4c","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"baf1e1b922"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"c138e100be","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东以中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会主席的名义发布的指示。"},{"id":"3fd75e5b9d","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会主席毛泽东1950年8月1日发布的关于在军队中实施文化教育的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5e623d09a1","type":"title","text":"关于改变一九五一年部队教育时间比例的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"},{"id":"c138e100be","type":"paragraph","text":"军委曾于本年八月一日颁布指示，自一九五一年开始，全军教育以提高文化为首要任务。现为适应目前形势的发展，需要加紧部队的军事训练，特将部队训练教育的时间重新规定如下","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"},{"id":"3fd75e5b9d","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、各军区一般部队训练时间比重为：军事百分之六十，政治百分之三十，文化百分之十。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"},{"id":"1537cc8555","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、离职的速成中学：文化百分之八十，军事百分之十，政治百分之十。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"},{"id":"99a954add7","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、某些起义部队：须要继续改造者，可规定政治百分之六十，军事百分之三十，文化百分之十","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"},{"id":"9ab8d982ad","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、各军事学校：按各学校计划执行。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"},{"id":"543eba6e91","type":"paragraph","text":"主席毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"},{"id":"51d9f5bb59","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年十二月三日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922"}],"page":{"id":"ff3b40e794","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"baf1e1b922","start":412,"end":412}}}},"__N_SSG":true}